{"tid":2431640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"哈里專訪｜梅根被指密謀今次專訪達兩年 被控「欺凌」皇室職員白金漢宮「十分關注」","createTime":"2021-03-03T20:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T07:12:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8cafe039719f23aae4b4ecd0cedd9ede691482","tid":2431640,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:31:12.000Z","msg":"哈里王子與夫人梅根接受美國名嘴奧花雲費專訪，這場備受矚目的訪談即將於本月7日播出，同時惹來大量批評聲音。節目將播出前，有英國傳媒引述匿名消息人士指，梅根仍是皇室成員時曾經欺凌皇室職員，但哈里夫婦一方否認。另有英媒指，梅根在兩年前長子阿奇出生後，已經打算接受其荷李活好友金格（Gayle King）專訪，雖然當時遭白金漢宮拒絕，但梅根一直未放棄受訪計劃，籌備近兩年後終與奧花雲費合作進行訪談。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210304/RKZAQ62RRNA5JMFZQ6SMKSD2EM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210304%2FRKZAQ62RRNA5JMFZQ6SMKSD2EM%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=33d671a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210304%2FRKZAQ62RRNA5JMFZQ6SMKSD2EM%2F&h=2199c4bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210304/RKZAQ62RRNA5JMFZQ6SMKSD2EM/</a>"},{"pid":"a901ffcaf415406c54b8e705f4a4281dde89d120","tid":2431640,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:33:54.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c14540a8b62d125c7943a3a938359e0e90838973","tid":2431640,"uid":364767,"like":1,"dislike":90,"score":-89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:35:52.000Z","msg":"痴線！<br />\n皇室欺凌meghan markle咋下話？"},{"pid":"14dcff2a4440653f882f96d105ae403fb85dfb05","tid":2431640,"uid":349494,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T20:48:15.000Z","msg":"戥佢啲仔女慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f432184280cb8a52c6b6528953aab7764be6c7","tid":2431640,"uid":133806,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T22:47:30.000Z","msg":"Our lives our way 就唔好再黐住個皇室名銜啦<br />\n<br />\n一邊話要自主，一邊又想黐家族金腔，邊有得咁著數㗎"},{"pid"